title: Week 3 recap
itunes:title: Week 3 recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Colleen Wolfe – break down each game from week 3 of the regular season including the Ravens falling to 0-3 and the Seahawks getting their first win in 2015.
